	<h1 class="title">太贵了，“莆田系”医院想放弃买百度竞价排名了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/2007/small/2007.jpg?1408114682" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">许冰清</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-03-26 14:56:29 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7811/medium/7811.jpg?1436693773" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="7811" data-title="《太贵了，“莆田系”医院想放弃买百度竞价排名了》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/7811/medium/7811.jpg?1436693773" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/7811.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
	<div class="share-bd clearfix">
